Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for such a lovely introduction. It is, of course, a great pleasure to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,today and to meet with such a wonderful audience. We do have some slides which will help us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,explain things with a visual assist. The information which I came upon which resulted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in the writing of Power vs. Force was an astonishing discovery. For the first time in all of human
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,history,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:01:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there evolved the way to discover truth from falsehood, a statement that is so stunning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure nobody in the audience understands it. It took some years to recover from it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,five years, in which I tried to decide what to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was discovered that consciousness itself records all that ever occurs, mentally, emotionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,physically. Everything that has ever happened has been recorded throughout all of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all of what we experience as time. On the level of consciousness, there is no time. There
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:02:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is no time. So everything is recorded as though all of the past is present. We could
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,recover anything about anything that had happened anywhere in time or space, but we could not
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,tell anything about the future. Using the Kinesiologic test, we could discover anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that is or was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could not be used to foretell the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The consequence of discovering how to tell truth from falsehood, then, ended up in calibrating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness from one to a thousand. One is bare physical existence. And we asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the most advanced consciousness that has ever existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness that has ever existed on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And we got calibration level 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually the numbers were far greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore we ended up using the logarithm of the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We ended up with a usable scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,much like Fahrenheit, centigrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody can make up their own scale if they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,On everybody's scale, no matter what you make it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be at a point that differentiates truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the kinesiologic test, which I first saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. John Diamond back in the early 70s, I believe it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,up to that time it was thought to be a local phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold asparagus over your solar plexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you're allergic to it, your arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thought of as a local phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But by the time I saw it, I had already had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a number of rather extraordinary transformations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw it from a whole different viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was obvious that it was the energy of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as consciousness that was responding to the question
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the individual person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we found that the response to the question,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the individual person, and so we found that the response to the question,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the response to the question,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the response to the question,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the kinesiologic test,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,had nothing to do with the personal opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And this morning we were asked to demonstrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll show you briefly how to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristic of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that life knows that which is supportive of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,much like protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an impersonal response,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,much like protoplasm knows that which is not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and much like protoplasm knows that which is not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,disfavorable to it and that was inimicable and so using this simple test
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we were then able to go back over human history calibrate the level of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness of anything and everything that ever existed every writer every
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,philosopher every spiritual teacher every movie every writer every
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,philosopher were able to do countries and continents what appeared then is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,though the history of mankind was two-dimensional black and white and now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we had three-dimensional technicolor it brought for us awareness is not before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,impossible we found that if you hold something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,together you can change it and you can change it and you can change it and you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,can change it and you can change it and you can change it and you can change it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is true in mind the arm of the subject that you using goes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is true in mind the arm of the subject that you using goes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,strong and if it's false the arm goes weak
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,this does not have to be verbalized so Susan and I will show you exactly how to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,do it it's very quick and easy there's no point to try and complicate it in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,your mind it's very very simple that which is supportive of life and true makes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you go strong. That which is inimicable and false allows your arm to go weak. It's not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a true or false response. It's true or not true. The universe cannot respond with no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only respond to yes, collapse the wave function, and the resulting Dirac equation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,tells you the new state of the universe. So, it coincides quite well with the theory of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,quantum mechanics and advanced theoretical physics as well. My own personal experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which I'll have to give you a bit, otherwise some of the things I say will sound strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll sound strange anyway, but rather extraordinary experiences begin to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime, what the world calls this lifetime, at age three. At age three, out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of complete oblivion, from oblivion, from absolute nothingness, suddenly there was a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,severe shock-like experience, a sudden intense awareness of existence. Out of nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly there was existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Existence as such, the knowingness of existence, which at age three was non-verbal, no words
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for such an experience. But the confrontation with existence was profound and stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortly after, there suddenly came into awareness the possibility then, that there was no existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was no existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a duality of non-existence, that it might have come about, that it might not
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,have come about, this existence. And so, there was the polarity, the duality, of existence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,versus non-existence, which actually doesn't get resolved until consciousness level 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that was the presentation of the task of this lifetime, to transcend. The ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is allness or nothingness, existence versus non-existence. And beyond a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness, which calibrates at 600, one remembers what the world calls previous
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetimes. They're not previous lifetimes, but the world calls them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And one remembers the lifetime of Hinayana Buddhism, in which the ultimate reality was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,void. Consequently, at each physical death, this entity went into the void. Now, what
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you hold in mind is what you experience. But the void is not the ultimate reality, or you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,could stay there. And if the void were the ultimate reality, who would be there to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd be nothing to recall it. So, the confrontation, then, was with the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,truth. Confrontation with what is the ultimate truth, which became something of an obsession
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime. As a teenager, as a teenager, then, I had a severely exhausting life. I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,had an 18 mile paper route in Wisconsin. Ten below zero blizzard, pitch black, miles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from home, no electricity on the highway. And to get out of the wind, I dug into a big
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,snow bank. Ten below zero blizzard and pitch black. And I climbed into this hole in the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,snow. And a profound, incredible, crazy dream came to me that night. I had an incredible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,peace. Replace whatever illusion there was of a personal self. An infinite, exquisite
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,peace. Its presence is unmistakable, exquisitely gentle, melts. It melts what one thinks of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:11:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,as oneself. And it's diffused, it's like the presence of love on an absolute level. Which
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,goes on outside of time, experientially, perhaps eons. Because that which I am existed before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,all universes and will still be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is apparently clear. It's like the profound essence of the knowingness. And subsequent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience, the fear of death has never recurred. Including during the war, the real
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,war II. Mines are going off. I was on a minesweeper, and there was never even the попыт także
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,15.ые
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,thought of death to this day there's no thought of death there's no response to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,sudden loud noises so there seem to be alterations of the way in which life is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced my father came in our 1929 model a Ford and discovered my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,whereabouts and he seemed perturbed and I realized that if I didn't come back in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the body and breathe again I didn't breathe the body there was no desire to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,breathe the body in fact there hasn't been any desire to breathe it since but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway it breathes I said that he believed in death oh and that if I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't reprieve and re-energize the body whatever you want to call it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that he would think I died they would take away the body and bury it and my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:13:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,father would grieve so I love my father a great deal and so I made the mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing the body again and saved him the grief anyway that was so there was a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,series of such experiences you know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and that led to sort of a we'll skip over a number of such experiences but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there was always difficulty in maintaining a sense of a personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because it kept dissolving into an infinite presence and I would have to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,focus on being Dave and you're sitting here in this chair in this classroom and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging on to the personal self you know it seemed elusive
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mental with having lost control about myself for years and years and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then 19 looked all I was taken care of i belt and he was like oh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you're this young to carry around all these different things and chopped off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotional links and thoughts and all that and then there seemed to be I was a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,very religious young man brought a pipes episode oh very very religious and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,scrupulous in fact and one day it's some time in my early life I was walking along in the woods it was absolutely beautiful and still and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,arose a revelation, a comprehension
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of the totality of the suffering of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time in its totality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The totality of its agony and fear and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that instant, I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I held God responsible for the totality of human suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the human ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that time, I did not understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought God created everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,1930s religion, that would be a common belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody spoke about the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They only spoke about sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I didn't realize that this was the creation of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And frankly, it was a great relief to get away from sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't worry that a passing thought
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,might condemn you to hell forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was a devout...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a devout atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a Jesuit university and got straight A
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in theology, ethics, metaphysics, the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Later on, I went through psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had, in fact, the largest psychiatric practice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000 outpatients.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000 new patients a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,50 employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,25 offices.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Electroencephalographic laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinical laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Research laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We had one of the first computers available.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a giant thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It stood in a room of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to genuflect to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Had to be air conditioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Special cables of electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a wondrous machine
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to do our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, all of this intensity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize the essential core and truth of existence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,persisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet finally, this huge practice
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the seeing of thousands of patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, thousands of patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the most severe conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the pressure of trying to help so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to develop all kinds of psychosomatic illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, the desire to know the truth then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,came back with a greater intensity than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I despaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I despaired of being able to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,realize the essential core of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The great books of the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated about 460.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aristotle, Plotinus, comes the closest, Plotinus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You go through all of the great minds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that have every existed they're in like,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the great psychoanalysts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The great philosophers, the great thinkers of all time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and it wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Philosophy takes you to theology.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To metaphysics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,physics, Gnosis, G-N-O-S-I-S, still not there. It's not there. I'll save you time. Read books
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Western World, calibrated 460. If you're looking for the absolute truth, you become
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,educated, but you won't find what is the core of the absolute truth. And so I went into
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation, and I dove within myself. And then I found the way to hell. And the doors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:19:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to hell opened up, and I began to descend into hell. How Dante knew the details of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,precisely, how does he know it? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the upper level, they're chopping people up in torture and all what the world considers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,hell. That part is just a joke. That's just jacks for openers. That's just weird saying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,hi. And from there, the despair deepens. It gets blacker and blacker. And the agony is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how Dante knew it, I don't know. But there is actually a level where you leave time and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,go into timelessness. And there's a knowingness, a knowingness. Abandon all hope, ye who enter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,here. And by God, it is. So then agony of endless hopelessness goes on for yon. And it's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond despair, far worse than despair. I was an atheist at the time. And somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from somewhere, came the question, if there is a God, I ask him to help me. And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,oblivion. Oblivion. And then, with the return of consciousness, with the return of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,some time later, all had been transformed, which it is to this day. The mind was silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the incredible magnificence of divinity shines forth, is all of creation. It shines
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thusly, now. The mind still. And I noticed that the body kept moving. The body moved
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,about by itself. As you can see, it still does. Does its own thing, like some kind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything happens spontaneously. It is not everything. Everything happens spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no personal self causing anything to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All that personal self we worry about does not even have any existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What must God think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep praying about this thing that has no existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks, human beings are so pathetic, what can we do for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, since that time, everything happens spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cause of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no thought going on at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no knowing what's going to be said until I hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that thinks what it's going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It just says it, because it is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how to function in the world in that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what the body is going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to behave properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to say the correct things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I left the East in a very elite lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.05,0:23:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.55,0:23:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I took my tools from the tool room, put them in the back of my truck, and drove away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Drove out to a small town and went into about 10 years or so of withdrawal from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that led to this kind of research, which we're reporting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, there are certain things that, once you've heard them, are transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain information is, in and of itself, transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I'll give you the crux of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to these charts in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, who are the people on the planet who transcend the consciousness level of the 400?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.81,0:24:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,4% of the population ever transcends consciousness level 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,499 is the level of Freud, Einstein, Sir Isaac Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.46,0:24:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,499 is intellectual brilliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.20,0:24:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.70,0:24:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the intellect, which is, in a way, the savior of mankind with science, science has certainly brought us great benefits,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.38,0:24:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,now becomes the ceiling, now becomes the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And very few people escape the snare of the mind and thinking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape the duality of thinking there is a this causing a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.42,0:24:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the secret of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.70,0:25:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Save you 500 lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar each lifetime, so you think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.70,0:25:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, listen to this and don't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.70,0:25:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just know that it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm karmically responsible for saying this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.70,0:25:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm fully aware of that responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cause for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.70,0:25:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.70,0:25:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.70,0:25:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.70,0:25:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.70,0:25:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.70,0:25:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how do things come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.70,0:25:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.70,0:25:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's nothing causing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.70,0:25:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's nothing causing this talkingness, which is going on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.70,0:25:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.70,0:25:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.70,0:26:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll have to explain the universe a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.70,0:26:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we look at divinity as a field of infinite power with no limitations and no dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This infinite field of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.70,0:26:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Power contrasts with force.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.70,0:26:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Force is linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.70,0:26:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Understandable through Newtonian physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.70,0:26:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The differential calculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.70,0:26:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Power is beyond that realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.70,0:26:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Power is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Has no beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.70,0:26:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Has no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does not go from here to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.70,0:26:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not measurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.70,0:26:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Power is more like gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.70,0:26:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Power just stands there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.70,0:27:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Power influences all within its realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.70,0:27:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uses up no energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.70,0:27:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.70,0:27:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything within its field is influenced by the quality of the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.70,0:27:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.70,0:27:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.70,0:27:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is within its field we're familiar with in the linear Newtonian world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.70,0:27:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Identifiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.70,0:27:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, space and location.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.70,0:27:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the human consciousness as it evolves then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.70,0:27:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Through its own spiritual decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.70,0:27:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings about its own you might say configuration or energy level.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:28:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You might picture we're like infinitely small molecules or little microns.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.70,0:28:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Little tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.70,0:28:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have a polarity and we have a figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.70,0:28:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So every spiritual decision we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.70,0:28:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual will then.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.70,0:28:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sets up you might say our karmic vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.70,0:28:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our karmic vibrational pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.70,0:28:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Which goes on beyond time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.70,0:28:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And within the infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.70,0:28:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.70,0:28:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.70,0:28:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.70,0:28:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then each.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.70,0:28:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.70,0:28:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpuscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.70,0:28:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.70,0:28:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.70,0:28:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.70,0:28:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.70,0:28:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.70,0:28:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.70,0:28:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is all about the power of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.70,0:28:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the world goes automatically to where.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.70,0:28:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would go in such a powerful field.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.70,0:28:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We see then that the justice of God is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.70,0:29:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that every iron filing is exactly in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In this infinite field of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.70,0:29:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And it could, cannot be in any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.70,0:29:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A judgmental, arbitrary, dualistic kind of a conception of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.86,0:29:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,who gets angry, mad, judgmental, punishes, rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that the justice of God is absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.05,0:29:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and that each comes into his own exactly depending on his own vibrational level.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.12,0:29:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it leaves the physical body at what the world calls physical depth,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.27,0:29:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it automatically is in its perfect position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.89,0:29:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in anger, you can protest, man the barricades,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.98,0:29:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,demand something better for yourself, protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.48,0:30:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got enough energy at least to come out of apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.05,0:30:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Apathy, which characterizes good parts of Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.27,0:30:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,People, children seldom live beyond age five.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.61,0:30:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If they lived to adulthood, they're dead by 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.83,0:30:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,AIDS and disease and poverty and starvation,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.03,0:30:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,avitaminosis, ravages.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.01,0:30:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you manage to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.96,0:30:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then the internal civil wars which go on for decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.68,0:30:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you manage to live to adulthood, you probably get slaughtered anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.31,0:30:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is not so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.85,0:30:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.85,0:30:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that above anger, pride now has to do with accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.51,0:30:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So first you're in despair, you're in apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.59,0:30:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then hope arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.24,0:31:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that even fear brings a person out of the bottom of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.29,0:31:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor old lady rocking in the rocking chair doesn't even experience fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.29,0:31:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.00,0:31:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's too apathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.27,0:31:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear has a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.33,0:31:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run like the devil in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.31,0:31:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can really move a lot with anger and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.09,0:31:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You tend to do a few things and move up to pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.09,0:31:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,From pride, you then move above the level of integrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.83,0:31:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,level of 200, which is courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.29,0:31:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is, for the first time, a real spiritual dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.25,0:31:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those below are not spiritual dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.09,0:31:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.27,0:31:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,animal dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.81,0:31:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of 200, a person now has the capacity to tell the truth about themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.72,0:31:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.89,0:31:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.33,0:31:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am addicted to alcohol and drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.59,0:32:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am ruining the lives of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.87,0:32:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of denial and projection, one now has power.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.16,0:32:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.96,0:32:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,200,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.44,0:32:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is the beginning of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.31,0:32:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's characteristic of the first step in the 12-step group,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.03,0:32:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,from which millions of people have recovered from all kinds of grave and curable illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.44,0:32:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The first step is owning the truth about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.37,0:32:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Left to your own devices, your condition is hopeless and undoubtedly fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.72,0:32:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the help of some higher power.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.96,0:32:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's an honest statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.89,0:32:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,An honest statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.81,0:32:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.31,0:32:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.81,0:32:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from many,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.27,0:32:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,many,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.77,0:32:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.05,0:32:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.33,0:32:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've witnessed recovery from almost every possible human ailment through spiritual means.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.27,0:32:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Course of miracles, 12 steps, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.03,0:32:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning is the admission that in and of one's self, one lacks the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.27,0:33:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That calibrates the 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.98,0:33:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.48,0:33:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and up are the beginnings of spiritual power and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.66,0:33:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We see,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.79,0:33:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,some courage and next move up is letting go of consequences, neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.75,0:33:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop living out of the anxiety of the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.16,0:33:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And in neutral, you become an easy going person.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,People of,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.11,0:33:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.98,0:33:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.81,0:33:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,are comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.59,0:33:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, these people are the first comfortable people, you're not really comfortable if you get up from neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.72,0:33:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In neutral, if you get the job it's terrific,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.84,0:33:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't, you'll get another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.28,0:33:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.54,0:33:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So neutral is comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.44,0:33:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're easy people to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.10,0:33:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not trying to prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.84,0:33:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want to sell you their belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.86,0:33:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not proselytizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.86,0:33:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not into war.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.64,0:33:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not into conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.68,0:34:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're easygoing people in neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.12,0:34:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The next step up is willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.76,0:34:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.20,0:34:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness now is more than just being neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.86,0:34:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The waitress in neutral says, what do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.60,0:34:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't really care that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.32,0:34:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave a tip or not if you do as great and if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.38,0:34:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But she probably doesn't look you in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.46,0:34:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She takes your order and she says, what do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.51,0:34:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She does her job and she's in neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.94,0:34:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The next step up is friendliness and willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.88,0:34:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The waitress in willingness makes,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.84,0:34:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a good deal more money than the waitress in neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.36,0:34:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the waitress in neutral is somewhat flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.28,0:34:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In willingness, there is more of the personal presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.76,0:34:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You smile at the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.76,0:34:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, can I have the same thing as usual, George?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.76,0:34:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels at home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.72,0:34:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes twice as much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.68,0:35:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's twice the tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.51,0:35:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Her customers come back to her and want to sit at her table.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.20,0:35:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's friendly and nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.48,0:35:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She remembers their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.03,0:35:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She becomes Georgette or whatever her name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You look forward to seeing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.60,0:35:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how new energy has,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.36,0:35:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of love is beginning to show up as this willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.86,0:35:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And acceptance is now where you begin to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.55,0:35:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are the source of the details of your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.42,0:35:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop blaming it on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.68,0:35:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Down below, people blame everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.74,0:35:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The slip on the ice is Gimbal's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.64,0:35:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As you get a little bit higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.82,0:35:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize you're careless in where you put your feet, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.80,0:35:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to accept responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.20,0:35:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's the beginning of real power.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.22,0:35:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrate companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.55,0:36:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrate thousands of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.36,0:36:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, we did all the biggest corporations in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.78,0:36:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest corporations in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.84,0:36:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest corporations in America, in Fortune Magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.72,0:36:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done all the departments of all the various governments, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.03,0:36:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And rather amazing facts begin to reveal themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.05,0:36:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That almost all the giant corporations in the world calibrate maybe 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.70,0:36:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarce, you'll find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.01,0:36:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.48,0:36:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Reliable, dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.32,0:36:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You paid $20,000 for a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.78,0:36:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.18,0:36:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a guaranteed car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.03,0:36:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get a fake car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.74,0:36:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You get what you paid for.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.74,0:36:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's integrity, honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.74,0:36:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Most government agencies calibrate around 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.40,0:36:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that's not airy-fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.94,0:36:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not lovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.74,0:36:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.98,0:36:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But that isn't what you're paying for, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.14,0:37:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Invest your money in a stock and say, I want profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.74,0:37:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You get higher than that, then you have to add a new element.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.60,0:37:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendliness, integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Willing to stand by your product.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.34,0:37:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give you back your money smilingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.94,0:37:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.44,0:37:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I got corresponding with Sam Walton.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.22,0:37:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was Sam Walton.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.05,0:37:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Establishing a business based on certain premises,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.38,0:37:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which are generally considered spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.01,0:37:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we corresponded back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.10,0:37:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the book, Harvard is for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.12,0:37:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I calibrated Walmart at 385 or 365.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.78,0:37:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.84,0:37:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not staggeringly high when you compare it to a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.03,0:37:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But Walmart doesn't claim to be a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.92,0:37:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But at 365, then, it's gone down somewhat since Sam died,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.80,0:37:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but still it's way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.46,0:37:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in its class.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.98,0:38:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In all the corporations in the world, nothing is in the 300s.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.68,0:38:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is really in the high 200s, only Walmart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.92,0:38:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does that demonstrate to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.76,0:38:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anything about Walmart, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.66,0:38:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that integrity, that integrity then,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.94,0:38:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,shows up in every area of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.84,0:38:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So here was a corporation whose integrity was remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.20,0:38:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I remarked about it in Harvard is for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.60,0:38:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we see what integrity has brought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.72,0:38:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That integrity, it is now the largest corporation in the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.76,0:38:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The largest corporation in the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.53,0:38:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And also the highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.84,0:38:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest calibrated level of consciousness of an enterprise of a corporate nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.24,0:38:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Demonstrating, then, that the power of integrity shows up on the bottom line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.84,0:39:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and is not some kind of airy-fairy, do-gooder, goody-two-shoes kind of fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.46,0:39:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the hard-boiled businessman, a lot of spiritual concepts, sounds a little airy-fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.16,0:39:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Touchy-feely.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.84,0:39:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me any touchy-feely, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.48,0:39:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.42,0:39:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, caringness, consideration, friendliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.40,0:39:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does the jacket say when you walk into Walmart?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.50,0:39:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, how can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.50,0:39:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right out of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.03,0:39:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Helpfulness, willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.32,0:39:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So then we finally get to reason and logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.05,0:39:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where Northern Europe, the United States, advanced civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.84,0:39:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as countries calibrated in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.72,0:39:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.82,0:39:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The great benefit of the intellect towards we witness every day as the advances of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.40,0:39:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Few of us would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.03,0:39:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd all be dead of various diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.80,0:40:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of science, all the diseases I treated when I first started in medicine some 50 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.07,0:40:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.22,0:40:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The infectious disease hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.96,0:40:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.74,0:40:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.82,0:40:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.96,0:40:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people sick and dying of various diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.98,0:40:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no antibiotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.10,0:40:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to cure them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.70,0:40:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, all those people would be living, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.36,0:40:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the 400s is the world of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.01,0:40:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The university.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.00,0:40:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The college professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.86,0:40:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The 400s are presidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.66,0:40:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Statesmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.03,0:40:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Court justices.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.28,0:40:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.96,0:40:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobel Prize winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.18,0:40:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually the high 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.84,0:40:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To be president of a huge country then requires intellectual fortitude and great education.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.10,0:40:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So they almost all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.78,0:40:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the presidents throughout time have been in the high 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.05,0:41:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,From 500 up, a person wouldn't be interested in being president.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.09,0:41:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,500 and up, then, is the opening of the heart chakra and the energy field of love that's calibrating at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.53,0:41:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At 540 is the level of unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.42,0:41:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of 500 and up in itself is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.46,0:41:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,4% of the population ever calibrates at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.77,0:41:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,0.4 calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.07,0:41:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.51,0:41:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show the distribution of the levels of consciousness in the population in the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.21,0:42:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Love becomes then progressively unconditional, finally saintly, and at the level 600, the personal self dissolves into a oneness, and that is the state of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.21,0:42:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The states of enlightenment begin at 600, what the world calls enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.21,0:42:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.71,0:42:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.03,0:42:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.05,0:42:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.17,0:42:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.32,0:42:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One in 10 million lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.38,0:42:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One in 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.00,0:42:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Never reaches 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.23,0:42:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And of those who do, only half will stay in the world in that condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.73,0:42:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to breathe or to eat or to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.61,0:42:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is absolutely perfect, complete, and still.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.13,0:42:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond time, beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.11,0:42:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no thinkingness, no thought, no desire for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.38,0:42:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,People do strange things. They want you to eat and all kinds of oddities, which to them seem
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.18,0:42:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,important. So you eat because it's important to them. So you eat because it's important to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.70,0:43:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because otherwise the body falls over, which is irrelevant, by the way. As love becomes more
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.94,0:43:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,perfected then, one comes into various progressive states, which are familiar to sainthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.01,0:43:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a state of, at about 540, one falls in love with everything and everyone. The beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.26,0:43:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of everything and its perfection shines forth. Everyone is both either handsome or beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.50,0:43:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as the case may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.94,0:43:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or both. Handsomely beautiful and beautifully handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.50,0:43:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One falls in love with everyone and everything, all of life. And you see what is emerging then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.34,0:43:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is the awareness of the divinity of all of life, and one develops a certain reverence.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.01,0:44:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of love we're speaking of is not what the world calls love. It's the world
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.94,0:44:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,calls love is an emotion, an emotionality, which goes from here to there. I love you. You love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.70,0:44:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Which is the setup for murder and suicide, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.86,0:44:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I love you and you love me, I will kill you or kill myself. So murder and suicide is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.50,0:44:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the downside of that kind of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.94,0:44:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Love has a vacuous dimension, which means love is also conditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.05,0:44:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.42,0:44:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of love we're talking about then is the way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.26,0:44:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At 540, that calibrated level, love is what one is, what one has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.57,0:45:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no love that goes from here to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.98,0:45:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the condition in which you experience
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.05,0:45:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, there's a reverence and respect for all of life and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.82,0:45:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As the love advances, it comes to a state which can only be called ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.00,0:45:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In the higher level of love, to even look at two people who are affectionate towards
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.53,0:45:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,each other, you can break out in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.11,0:45:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You break out in tears, so there's a period in which you cry at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.40,0:45:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Every kind gesture, mother reaches over to touch her crying child and comfort it, and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.23,0:45:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you break out in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.88,0:45:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything makes you break out in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.42,0:45:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to listen to beautiful music because you cry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.42,0:46:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that, there's a level of love which can only be described as ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.11,0:46:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Described by Ramakrishna, experienced in this lifetime, one of absolute ecstasy beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.07,0:46:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,description, in which it's impossible almost not to dance physically or psychically.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.05,0:46:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One is in ecstasy at the revelation of the presence of God as all existence, ecstatic
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.69,0:46:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when its first reveals itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.11,0:46:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to function in that state of ecstasy, and by divine inspiration, one
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.25,0:46:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,may surrender it to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.33,0:47:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One surrenders the ecstasy to God, and then, in its place, is a profound and infinite peace
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.67,0:47:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.11,0:47:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you see this this totally spiritual place, one looks only for the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.75,0:47:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,end of what is needed, even again, toalah heavenly, then illusive, while life continues
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.27,0:47:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to 하는 peace, Этот ihr ringing lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.00,0:47:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So your expectation and all
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.01,0:47:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,род mitä kehara ekspozis takitah mitra maem'ikros.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.15,0:47:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a distribution of the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.13,0:47:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, your expectations of humanity have never been tailored by any kind of realistic
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.57,0:47:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.57,0:47:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this is the distribution of the levels of consciousness throughout all of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.11,0:47:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, one can revise one's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.11,0:47:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time of the Neanderthal man, consciousness level was about 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.11,0:47:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How many kept evolving off the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.11,0:48:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, it got up into the low 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.11,0:48:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time of the birth of the Buddha, the consciousness level of all of mankind stood at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.11,0:48:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time of the birth of Jesus Christ, the consciousness level of all of mankind stood at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.11,0:48:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout the ensuing centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.11,0:48:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness level of man crept up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.11,0:48:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then for the last thousand years, it stood at 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.11,0:48:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalled out at 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.11,0:48:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask, what was it in the 1400s? We'll get 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.11,0:48:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it in the 1500s? What was it in the 1600s?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.11,0:48:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, many of these buildings here were built in the 1600s.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.11,0:48:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of mankind was 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.11,0:48:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's below truth, below integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.11,0:49:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the history of mankind is bloody and savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.11,0:49:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The history of Europe is bloody savagery.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.11,0:49:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First this side wars and butchers them, and this side wars and butchers that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.11,0:49:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they get busy beheading each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.11,0:49:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bloody and horrible history. Look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.11,0:49:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last century, 10 million people have died of this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.11,0:49:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million, rather.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.11,0:49:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, forgot one zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.11,0:49:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.11,0:49:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in the late 1980s, for unknown reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.11,0:49:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness level of mankind went from 190 to 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.11,0:49:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important phenomena in human history, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.11,0:49:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To go from non-integrity, that which is destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.11,0:49:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,like 190, eventually mankind would have destroyed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.11,0:50:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Russians were prepared to do it, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.11,0:50:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The great mega-bomb that would kill all of life on the planet forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.11,0:50:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Radioactivity. Death to humanity by radioactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.11,0:50:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too kindly a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.11,0:50:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.11,0:50:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the late 1980s, the consciousness level of mankind went up to 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.11,0:50:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.11,0:50:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.11,0:50:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because 207, you go strong with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.11,0:50:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At 190, you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.11,0:50:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With 207, there's hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.11,0:50:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At 190, the fate of mankind would be eventually its own obliteration.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.11,0:50:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason mankind didn't obliterate itself until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.11,0:50:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't have anything capable big enough to kill everybody all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.11,0:50:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Russians were busy working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.11,0:50:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We would have eventually done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.11,0:50:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.11,0:50:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here we see the distribution of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.11,0:51:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that 78% of the world's population at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.11,0:51:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,78%, calibrated below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.11,0:51:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's still a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.11,0:51:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's still a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.11,0:51:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.11,0:51:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Approximately 78% of the world's population calibrated below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.11,0:51:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.11,0:51:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.11,0:51:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the implications of that alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.11,0:51:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,78% of the world's population is non-integrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.11,0:51:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,believes in falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.11,0:51:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and will kill you if you don't believe in its falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.11,0:51:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.11,0:51:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's where mankind has evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.11,0:51:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at the present time,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.11,0:51:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say the collective good karma of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.11,0:51:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has brought about a progression in the consciousness level,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.11,0:52:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's at a hopeful 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.11,0:52:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could have the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.11,0:52:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The big difficulty in the evolution of consciousness is called duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.11,0:52:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway I teach is,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.11,0:52:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.11,0:52:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotion to God, to the truth of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.11,0:52:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and transcending the dualistic nature of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.11,0:52:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at which point the mind goes silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.11,0:52:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of duality is that there are two opposite things.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.11,0:52:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's heat and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.11,0:52:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's goodness and badness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.11,0:52:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Political left, political right,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.11,0:52:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,everything gets into a polarized duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.11,0:52:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, conflict and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.11,0:52:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The right versus the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.11,0:52:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One day I'm right, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.11,0:52:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day we trade off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.11,0:53:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at time, the right and the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.11,0:53:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two different lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.11,0:53:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at the map of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.11,0:53:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as it evolves over the centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.11,0:53:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you see light and wrong, light and wrong, right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.11,0:53:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it all flashing on it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.11,0:53:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This side's right, this side's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.11,0:53:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, two years later, this side's wrong and this side's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.11,0:53:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.11,0:53:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is World War II, we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.11,0:53:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They were our enemies. We hated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.11,0:53:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They were supposed to kill the terrible Japs, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.11,0:53:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them a gleaning evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.11,0:53:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, after the war, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.11,0:53:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the veterans on both sides are great buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.11,0:53:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.11,0:53:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I salute his bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.11,0:53:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He salutes my bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.11,0:53:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We both realized we did it for the sake of what we believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.11,0:53:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The commitment was,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.11,0:53:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to integrity, what we thought of as integrity at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.11,0:53:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.11,0:53:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that heals the disparity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.11,0:53:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't hate anybody anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.11,0:54:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.11,0:54:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And veterans of both sides
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.11,0:54:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,pray together, meet together, embrace each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.11,0:54:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and we realize
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.11,0:54:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.11,0:54:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the commitment to something greater than oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.11,0:54:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One may be mistaken at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.11,0:54:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll find that a kamikaze pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.11,0:54:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.11,0:54:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He did what he did
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.11,0:54:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because of his belief in the divinity of his emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.11,0:54:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.11,0:54:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.11,0:54:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, from an arbitrary viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.11,0:54:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we think there's hot and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.11,0:54:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's only the presence of heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.11,0:54:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's either heat present or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.11,0:54:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one variable, not two variables.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.11,0:54:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat is either present or not present.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.11,0:54:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, we can look at another scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.11,0:54:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,example two, in which you see
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.11,0:54:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to want a thing or not want a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.11,0:54:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you perceive a projected value,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.11,0:54:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which you project upon the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.11,0:55:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either precious and worthwhile
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.11,0:55:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.11,0:55:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love gold, you'll kill for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.11,0:55:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think it's just
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.11,0:55:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a, you know, pretty and useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.11,0:55:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be bothered because it's just sort of okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.11,0:55:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.11,0:55:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold means neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.11,0:55:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The bad is sort of useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.11,0:55:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stick things in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.11,0:55:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's have the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.11,0:55:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, other examples of duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.11,0:55:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See, goodness versus badness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.11,0:55:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,are all perceptual.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.11,0:55:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say perceptual,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.11,0:55:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the difficulty with the dualistic mind
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.11,0:55:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it has these belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.11,0:55:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which it then projects upon the world
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.11,0:55:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinks it sees it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.11,0:55:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It exists only within your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.11,0:55:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't exist in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.11,0:55:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this causality is an explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.11,0:55:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,made up by the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.11,0:55:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, evolution and creation
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.11,0:55:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.11,0:56:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If things don't come about by virtue of cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.11,0:56:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then how do they come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.11,0:56:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the existence of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.11,0:56:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the source of existence itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.11,0:56:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the great infinite power then,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.11,0:56:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the potentiality of each thing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.11,0:56:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to manifest its own actuality unfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.11,0:56:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing causing it to unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.11,0:56:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of that which one witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.11,0:56:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is the presence of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.11,0:56:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as the source of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.11,0:56:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The power.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.11,0:56:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring forth your own existence
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.11,0:56:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be found within the conceptual world.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.11,0:56:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality then,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.11,0:56:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by its karmic propensity,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.11,0:57:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolds as an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.11,0:57:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing it to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.11,0:57:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of cause is a mentation in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.11,0:57:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing causing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.11,0:57:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing causing this to happen whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.11,0:57:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality to use the body
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.11,0:57:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to explain a dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.11,0:57:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,does this of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.11,0:57:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.11,0:57:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as surprised by what the hand does as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.11,0:57:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it's doing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.11,0:57:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's trying to explain something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.11,0:57:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.11,0:57:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if karmically balanced under the right conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.11,0:57:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has the possibility then to become an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.11,0:57:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what seems to be sequential,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.11,0:57:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing that's sequential is perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.11,0:58:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your perception goes from here to there,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.11,0:58:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you think things are happening sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.11,0:58:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The witnessing is what is sequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.11,0:58:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The actuality is outside of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.11,0:58:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside of time to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.11,0:58:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were not so,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.11,0:58:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,no one here would exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.11,0:58:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.11,0:58:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it sounds pomposity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.11,0:58:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what we said is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.11,0:58:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That things come into actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.11,0:58:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,out of their potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.11,0:58:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the presence of the infinite divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.11,0:58:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite power of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.11,0:58:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only possible source of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.11,0:59:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we just got rid of duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.11,0:59:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll move to the next exciting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.11,0:59:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, well, I can't get rid of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.11,0:59:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I meditate. I'm a Buddhist.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.11,0:59:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm this, I'm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.11,0:59:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to transcend the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.11,0:59:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have lots of good news this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.11,0:59:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The other good news is that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.11,0:59:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,98% of your mind is silent at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.11,0:59:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, right this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.11,0:59:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,every single mind in this realm is silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.11,0:59:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is fall back into the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.11,0:59:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that the silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.11,0:59:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is already in existence just prior to the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.11,0:59:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was telling somebody this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.11,0:59:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha and I often have arguments about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.11,0:59:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Buddhists believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.11,0:59:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,reality can be glimpsed between two thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.11,0:59:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not between two thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.11,1:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just prior to the thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.11,1:00:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just prior to the thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.11,1:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a space of infinite silence
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.11,1:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which thinkingness arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.11,1:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That which, out of which it arises is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.11,1:00:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, your mind right now is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.11,1:00:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind of everyone in this realm is currently silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.11,1:00:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a focus.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.11,1:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a huge coliseum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.11,1:00:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's gone. It's completely empty.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.11,1:00:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And over in the corner of the coliseum
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.11,1:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is a four by five inch black and white TV set.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.11,1:00:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're focused on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.11,1:00:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think the coliseum,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.11,1:00:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the coliseum is busy and noisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.11,1:00:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty and silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.11,1:00:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're focused on this little screen
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.11,1:00:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,over in the corner of the coliseum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.11,1:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we discovered is that your mind is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.11,1:00:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,98% of the work you need to become enlightened
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.11,1:00:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is already done.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.11,1:01:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only got 2% left.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.11,1:01:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.11,1:01:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody can have 2%.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.11,1:01:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When we go wanting to think,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.11,1:01:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.11,1:01:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so we see that one is addicted to thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.11,1:01:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the real secret,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.11,1:01:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the real secret
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.11,1:01:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you've become hypnotized
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.11,1:01:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by the 1% that's talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.11,1:01:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,1 or 2%.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.11,1:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in a state of self-hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.11,1:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a secret
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.11,1:01:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which a lot of you will move rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.11,1:01:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only 1 or 2% that's busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.11,1:01:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in a hypnotic state.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.11,1:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that is needed then
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.11,1:01:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.11,1:01:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you realize it,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.11,1:01:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not that difficult
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.11,1:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of the desire for the thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.11,1:01:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that's derived out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.11,1:01:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the payoff that you get from the ego?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.11,1:02:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.11,1:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and have the silence replace it,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.11,1:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it is only necessary to see what the ego is up to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.11,1:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and be willing to surrender its payoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.11,1:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.11,1:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is not based on reality or love,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.11,1:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has managed to juice pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.11,1:02:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ego lives off
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.11,1:02:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the non-love,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.11,1:02:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,non-reality then
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.11,1:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of pain, suffering, guilt,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.11,1:02:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling right, feeling righteous.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.11,1:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see what it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.11,1:02:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It polarizes everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.11,1:02:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It politicizes everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.11,1:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can be contentious
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.11,1:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel so good and so right
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.11,1:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and see how wrong the other people are
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.11,1:02:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.11,1:02:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as you plunge a dagger into their heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.11,1:02:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're evil,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.11,1:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because you moralize
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.11,1:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.11,1:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are they evil?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.11,1:02:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you idealize
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.11,1:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and you hypothesize
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.11,1:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that they could be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.11,1:03:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we romanticize.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.11,1:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a wonderful world
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.11,1:03:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if everybody would just see things the way I see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.11,1:03:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And they don't, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.11,1:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why we criticize.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.11,1:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we feel upset about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.11,1:03:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we emotionalize.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.11,1:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a parade.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.11,1:03:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We dramatize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.11,1:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We make movies.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.11,1:03:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have parades.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.11,1:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.11,1:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.11,1:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look at any point in history,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.11,1:03:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,including the present time,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.11,1:03:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and discover that it's catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.11,1:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's catastrophic right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.11,1:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.11,1:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we theorize
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.11,1:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that it could be differently,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.11,1:03:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,could be different.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.11,1:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We rationalize why it's not different.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.11,1:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.11,1:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the tax money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.11,1:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We fantasize how it could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.11,1:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.11,1:03:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We infantilize things.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.11,1:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Intellectualize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.11,1:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.11,1:03:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,basically what we're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.11,1:03:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is mentalizing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.11,1:03:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We idealize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.11,1:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we glamorize the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.11,1:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't our ideas wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.11,1:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We make a drama.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.11,1:04:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We make a huge movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.11,1:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-five million dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.11,1:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.11,1:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,how I think or feel about something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.11,1:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The egocentricity of all
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.11,1:04:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is just staggering.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.11,1:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this is egocentricity
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.11,1:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing but.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.11,1:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what your ideas are?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.11,1:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.11,1:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.11,1:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.11,1:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you get into a discussion
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.11,1:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with somebody,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.11,1:04:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,take a moment and notice
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.11,1:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that they really don't give a rap
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.11,1:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're thinking
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.11,1:04:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or what your opinions are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.11,1:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They really don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.11,1:04:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.11,1:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if you present them with a platform,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.11,1:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if you present them with a platform
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.11,1:04:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,from which their ego can grandstand,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.11,1:04:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they can pontificate,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.11,1:04:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then they love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.11,1:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't give them a platform
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.11,1:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,upon which to pontificate,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.11,1:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they consider you boring.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.11,1:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And they will demonize you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.11,1:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of that
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.11,1:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as being bad and evil and ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.11,1:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.11,1:05:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we prize many things
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.11,1:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.11,1:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're willing to sacrifice a great deal
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.11,1:05:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for materialism.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.11,1:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the latest craze in society
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.11,1:05:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be the victim.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.11,1:05:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The competition in victimhood
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.11,1:05:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.11,1:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no aspect of human life
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.11,1:05:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that can't be portrayed
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.11,1:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as some kind of victimization,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.11,1:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which means there are evil people out there
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.11,1:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,victimizing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.11,1:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,People victimize me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.11,1:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They do it all day, every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.11,1:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think you're being victimized,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.11,1:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you just haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.11,1:05:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Every move,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.11,1:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you're being a victim
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.11,1:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of something or someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.11,1:05:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The government, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.11,1:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.11,1:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be through
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.11,1:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in about two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.11,1:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We will end abruptly.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.11,1:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The speaker will turn quickly
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.11,1:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on his heel and walk away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.11,1:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll know that's the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.11,1:06:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to just compare.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.11,1:06:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is viewed
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.11,1:06:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of causality,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.11,1:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian characteristic
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.11,1:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,world of science,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.11,1:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the intellect and logic,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.11,1:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which is on the left-hand side.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.11,1:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is logical,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.11,1:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,limitable,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.11,1:06:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,limited, provable,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.11,1:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to a greater,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.11,1:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,closer to reality
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.11,1:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in quantum mechanics,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.11,1:06:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,things are likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.11,1:06:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.11,1:06:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Provability is a figment
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.11,1:06:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.11,1:06:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.11,1:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing can be proven.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.11,1:06:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is provable.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.11,1:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not capacity.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.11,1:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that so?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.11,1:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the ultimate reality
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.11,1:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.11,1:06:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can be proven
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.11,1:06:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Newtonian paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.11,1:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only be realized
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.11,1:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,subjectively,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.11,1:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as the sense of the source
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.11,1:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.11,1:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot prove
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.11,1:07:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the existence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.11,1:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.11,1:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who lives
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.11,1:07:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the scientific,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.11,1:07:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,objective,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.11,1:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectual world
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.11,1:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,says that that is
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.11,1:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the only world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.11,1:07:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you know
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.11,1:07:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,why they say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.11,1:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because subjectively,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.11,1:07:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the truth to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.11,1:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute truth, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.11,1:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as you go beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.11,1:07:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,theology,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.11,1:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,systemology,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.11,1:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.11,1:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.11,1:07:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with the radical truth
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.11,1:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is subject,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.11,1:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,subjective.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.11,1:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the sense
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.11,1:07:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.11,1:07:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of your existence
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.11,1:07:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that is listening
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.11,1:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to the voice
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.11,1:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.11,1:07:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.11,1:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the source
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.11,1:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's own existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.11,1:07:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.11,1:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of God within.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.11,1:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.11,1:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.11,1:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's by permission
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.11,1:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the divinities within.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.11,1:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.11,1:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.11,1:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the right word.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.11,1:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By virtue
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.11,1:07:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.11,1:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of God within,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.11,1:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.11,1:07:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by permission
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.11,1:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the divinities
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.11,1:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,within,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.11,1:07:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.11,1:07:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.11,1:08:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of God within,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.11,1:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,one knows
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.11,1:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that one exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.11,1:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One is aware
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.11,1:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.11,1:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And to know
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.11,1:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that that source
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.11,1:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's existence
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.11,1:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.11,1:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of who one is,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.11,1:08:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is what is meant
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.11,1:08:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by self-realization.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.11,1:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.11,1:08:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.11,1:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.11,1:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.11,1:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.11,1:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.11,1:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.11,1:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.11,1:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.11,1:08:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.11,1:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,.
